snippet.title: Alien Hominid Invasion - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
https://www.alienhominidinvasion.com/game/  |  https://www.alienhominidinvasion.com/game/
Alien Hominid Invasion + Alien Hominid HD are now available on Steam, Xbox, and Nintendo Switch…this is not a drill, this is your boarding call! 

Old friends and bitter enemies await as you invade Earth alongside a Mothership full of alien friends! Blast, beam, and bite your way through an endless swarm of enemies as you and up to three of your fellow hominids cause mayhem with a huge arsenal of weapons, mutations, and acrobatic maneuvers. Invade with up to four players through online co-op, couch co-op, or both!
https://www.alienhominidinvasion.com/game/

If you’re looking for the purist Alien Hominid HD experience, it’s also now available on Steam, Xbox, and Nintendo Switch! Featuring updated graphics and quality of life fixes, enjoy the wonders of wood chippers or spend your days playing ALL the minigames!
https://www.alienhominidinvasion.com/game/

Music by Patric Catani: https://patric-catani.com/
